690
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:32,120
what a cross section is,
because this is a quantity

691
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:34,850
that you're going to
be using everywhere.

692
00:30:34,850 --> 00:30:37,130
Let's say that we fired
a beam of particles--

693
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:38,960
it doesn't matter what it is--

694
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,630
at a target of other particles.

695
00:30:41,630 --> 00:30:44,450
Let's say, the beam
