717
00:31:55,530 --> 00:31:57,990
ABn--

718
00:31:57,990 --> 00:32:01,180
which refers here to
the number density.

719
00:32:01,180 --> 00:32:03,150
So I'll keep our
table of symbols

720
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:05,265
altogether so it's a
little easier to follow.

721
00:32:05,265 --> 00:32:15,490
n is our number density, which
means the number of atoms

722
00:32:15,490 --> 00:32:17,740
per unit volume.

723
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:21,670
Usually, in nuclear
quantities, we use centimeters

724
00:32:21,670 --> 00:32:24,520
